    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Model Comparison\n",
        "\n",
        "This section summarizes the performance of all trained models in a comparison table.\n",
        "\n",
        "The purpose of the comparison table is to:\n",
        "- clearly show the MAE and RMSE of each model\n",
        "- identify the best-performing model\n",
        "- justify why one model is selected over another for future forecasting\n",
        "\n",
        "The model with the lower RMSE is selected as the best model because RMSE penalizes larger prediction errors more strongly. This makes it especially useful in forecasting tasks where extreme mistakes can distort business decisions."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "J7PMh3qM45Ej"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# ============================================================\n",
        "# 10) MODEL COMPARISON VISUALIZATION\n",
